INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (52,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:16','2015-02-16 20:40:16','Broadreach is the world leader in adventure and study-abroad programs for middle school, high school and college students. They offer more than 70 life-changing adventures in 40 countries where students can choose from a blend of college credit, community service hours and internationally recognized certifications. We created new positioning (“Broadreach. A new latitude.”) and developed an integrated online and offline marketing communications program to clearly differentiate Broadreach as a multidimensional alternative to typical teen travel.','Broadreach','','publish','closed','closed','','broadreach','','','2015-02-20 19:18:05','2015-02-20 19:18:05','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=52',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (53,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:16','2015-02-16 20:40:16','','Broadreach','','inherit','open','open','','52-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:40:16','2015-02-16 20:40:16','',52,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=53',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (54,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:22','2015-02-16 20:40:22','Cessna\'s 6,500 Citations are the largest fleet of business jet aircraft in the world, and more than half of all the aircraft flying today are Cessnas. At a cruise speed of up to Mach 0.935, the Citation X is the fastest civil (not built with tax dollars) airplane in the world. Cessna caters to a very discerning customer who can often face a number of complex specification decisions before taking delivery of the aircraft. We developed a customer-oriented communication program that outlined milestones, clarified the specification process and improved overall satisfaction among new Cessna owners — fostering a more direct connection and personal relationship with the brand.','Cessna Aircraft','','publish','closed','closed','','cessna','','','2015-02-20 19:17:36','2015-02-20 19:17:36','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=54',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (55,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:22','2015-02-16 20:40:22','','Cessna','','inherit','open','open','','54-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:40:22','2015-02-16 20:40:22','',54,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=55',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (56,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:29','2015-02-16 20:40:29','The Chums story was launched on the rapids of the Colorado River in the summer of \'82. Today, more than a million Chums Eyeglass Retention Devices are gripping the glasses of athletes and outdoor enthusiasts the world over. Success of the signature product led to the development and introduction of a new line of \"highly logical clothing\" called Hellowear. At the heart of the Chums brand is the promise of fun and functionality. The positioning, identity and B2C/B2B marketing programs we created not only reflect the company\'s unique, eccentric personality — they also expand the brand’s appeal to a whole new audience of enthusiasts.','Chums Outdoor Accessories','','publish','closed','closed','','chums','','','2015-02-20 19:18:45','2015-02-20 19:18:45','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=56',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (57,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:29','2015-02-16 20:40:29','','Chums','','inherit','open','open','','56-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:40:29','2015-02-16 20:40:29','',56,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=57',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (58,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:34','2015-02-16 20:40:34','MIT Sloan, the business school of the Massachusetts Institute of Technology, was established in 1914 and has become one of the world’s leading business schools, conducting cutting-edge research and providing management education to top students from more than 60 countries. Many of the world\'s most famous management and finance theories were developed at the school, and the faculty has included several Nobel laureates. We created an integrated visual identity program for alumni communication to reinforce brand values, clarify messaging and deepen alumni identification with this elite institution.','MIT Sloan School of Management','','publish','closed','closed','','mit','','','2015-02-20 19:19:25','2015-02-20 19:19:25','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=58',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (59,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:34','2015-02-16 20:40:34','','MIT','','inherit','open','open','','58-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:40:34','2015-02-16 20:40:34','',58,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=59',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (60,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:42','2015-02-16 20:40:42','The North Face started in 1966 as a small San Francisco retail and mail order operation catering to uncompromising outdoor purists. Within two years they were manufacturing their own gear, and over the past five decades have grown to become the industry leader in the design and manufacture of revolutionary outdoor equipment and clothing. Our challenge was to tell The North Face story in a way that would expand the brand\'s appeal without alienating the original enthusiasts whose support has been so critical to its success. Our solution positioned TNF as the clear industry leader, incorporating both right- and left-brain messaging delivered in a way that was relevant and accessible to all TNF stakeholders — novice and expert, retailer and consumer.','The North Face','','publish','closed','closed','','the-north-face','','','2015-02-20 19:14:28','2015-02-20 19:14:28','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=60',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (61,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:42','2015-02-16 20:40:42','','The North Face','','inherit','open','open','','60-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:40:42','2015-02-16 20:40:42','',60,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=61',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (62,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:51','2015-02-16 20:40:51','Over 25 years ago, luthier Ken Parker followed his calling to build and repair guitars. He’s worked with thousands of guitarists along the way, asking them to define their instruments\' best features and worst failings. Their input, combined with Ken\'s genius and craftsmanship, led to a radical new approach to the electric guitar called the Parker Fly. The innovative design was awarded 11 patents, paraded on the covers of guitar magazines, and exhibited at the Smithsonian — yet the Fly\'s sales fell far short of expectations. We worked with Parker to develop an integrated marketing approach that informed product development, clarified B2B communications, improved the buying experience and increased quarterly sales over 400%.','Parker Guitars','','publish','closed','closed','','parker-guitars','','','2015-02-20 19:20:03','2015-02-20 19:20:03','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=62',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (63,1,'2015-02-16 20:40:51','2015-02-16 20:40:51','','Parker Guitars','','inherit','open','open','','62-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:40:51','2015-02-16 20:40:51','',62,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=63',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (64,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:02','2015-02-16 20:41:02','Road Scholar (formerly Elderhostel) is the leading not-for-profit educational travel organization for more than 5 million adults who have participated in its 8,000 programs that are offered in all 50 U.S. states and 150 other countries. The organization\'s mission is to provide extraordinary access to learning and cultural experiences that open minds, touch hearts, and build bridges of understanding that can make the world a better place. We created new positioning (“Learning — It\'s a trip.”) and redesigned communication for both the domestic and international programs that speaks to both physical and cerebral wanderlust.','Road Scholar','','publish','closed','closed','','road-scholar','','','2015-02-20 19:21:29','2015-02-20 19:21:29','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=64',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (65,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:02','2015-02-16 20:41:02','','Road Scholar','','inherit','open','open','','64-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:41:02','2015-02-16 20:41:02','',64,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=65',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (66,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:08','2015-02-16 20:41:08','Segway is the number one provider of personal electric balancing transportation in the world. The zero-emissions Segway Personal Transporter delivers a very “green” energy efficiency equivalent of over 450 miles per gallon. We created new positioning (“Simply moving.”) and developed an integrated marketing program, including the development and design of both on and offline communications, that was successful in creating growth with early adopters and a wide range of niche commercial markets.','Segway','','publish','closed','closed','','segway','','','2015-02-20 19:22:01','2015-02-20 19:22:01','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=66',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (67,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:08','2015-02-16 20:41:08','','Segway','','inherit','open','open','','66-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:41:08','2015-02-16 20:41:08','',66,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=67',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (68,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:14','2015-02-16 20:41:14','For more than three decades, Thomson Safaris has been guiding travelers through Tanzania, the premier safari destination in Africa. This ecologically significant land encompasses a staggering amount and variety of wildlife that roam the iconic plains of the Serengeti and the lush green floor of the Ngorongoro Crater. Tanzania is also home to a diverse array of peoples and cultures united by a warm, generous spirit. The new positioning and marketing platform (“Our home. Your adventure.”) effectively differentiated the brand while succinctly addressing key consideration factors of an audience that values comfort and hospitality as well as adventure and authenticity.','Thomson Safaris','','publish','closed','closed','','thomson-safaris','','','2015-02-20 19:22:34','2015-02-20 19:22:34','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=68',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (69,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:14','2015-02-16 20:41:14','','Thomson Safaris','','inherit','open','open','','68-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:41:14','2015-02-16 20:41:14','',68,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=69',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (70,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:22','2015-02-16 20:41:22','When Robert Winston and his teenage son, Maynard, first wheeled their pushcart of flowers onto Boston\'s fashionable Newbury Street in 1944, they could not have foreseen that this humble enterprise would grow into a business that is recognized as one of the country\'s premier florists. Today, the third-generation, family-owned company has a worldwide online presence and seven retail locations throughout the Northeast, including the one right where it all began, on Newbury Street. Despite the company’s long history and loyal following, Winston Flowers struggled with customer perceptions that flowers are for “special occasions.” In order to encourage Winston enthusiasts to incorporate flowers into their everyday lives, and to help non-enthusiasts explore new and different occasions for purchase, we developed new positioning, refined identity and an integrated online/offline marketing program to align the online brand experience with the in-store brand experience.','Winston Flowers','','publish','closed','closed','','winston-flowers','','','2015-02-20 18:57:10','2015-02-20 18:57:10','',0,'https://saltworksinc.com/?post_type=sw_work&#038;p=70',0,'sw_work','',0);
INSERT INTO `SERVMASK_PREFIX_posts` VALUES (71,1,'2015-02-16 20:41:22','2015-02-16 20:41:22','','Winston Flowers','','inherit','open','open','','70-revision-v1','','','2015-02-16 20:41:22','2015-02-16 20:41:22','',70,'https://saltworksinc.com/?p=71',0,'revision','',0);
